   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(1st hand) Nikandros, son of Akousilaos, brewer of Theadelphia, to Horos, son of Mares, greetings. I have received, for the price of the beer, 5 obols on Tybi 25. On Mecheir 19, a payment of - dr.(?) On Pauni 20, a payment of 4 dr.</ab>
         </div>
